  "prompt": "What are some really good Korean spas in Minneapolis?",
  "response": "Minneapolis has several great options for Korean spas that offer a range of relaxing and rejuvenating services. Here are a few notable ones:\n\n1. **Aqua Spa & Sauna**: This spa offers a traditional Korean spa experience with various sauna options, hot tubs, and body scrubs. It's known for its clean facilities and relaxing atmosphere.\n\n2. **Spa 6**: Located in the heart of Minneapolis, Spa 6 provides a range of services including massages, facials, and body treatments, along with traditional Korean spa experiences.\n\n3. **Jiang's Spa**: This spa offers a mix of Korean and Chinese spa services, including herbal soaks, massages, and body scrubs. It's a good place to unwind and enjoy affordable services.\n\n4. **The Well Spa**: While not exclusively a Korean spa, The Well Spa incorporates some Asian-inspired treatments and offers a holistic approach to wellness.\n\n5. **Express Day Spa & Sauna**: This spa specializes in Korean-style body scrubs, massages, and has traditional sauna facilities. It's a cozy spot for a day of relaxation.\n\nBe sure to check the latest reviews and availability before visiting, as services and hours can change. Enjoy your spa experience!",
